OK Word for Windows fans try this:

Choose "Format"
Choose "Define Styles..."
Choose "Options>>"
In the Based on field enter "Normal"
Choose "OK"  for the error message
Cancel Define Styles
Choose Help
Choose "About..."
Turn Caps Lock on
Simultaneously hold down the O,P,U and S keys.

You should get a fireworks show and the authors of Word for Windows.   
It works for Version 1.1 dated July 3, 1990.
